oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Various Artist Recordings for a West-Vlaanderen, Belgium Radio Station
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Recording is of a radio station, believed to be hosted by Elsfan Herzelley, playing various country music hits . According to insert, tape originates from West-Vlannderen, Belgium. Recording is from October 5, 1972. Tape is number one of an unknown number.
